ComicInfo.Summary: The bloody end is here, and the vengeance of the pirates will be vicious and mighty! Jamie Delano cuts loose on a vicious pirate tale, delivering a bloody, terrifying vision of a world on the high-seas! The vicious Priests and his followers have taken to the worst forms of torture to get secrets from La Serena and her allies. But the final blow struck may not be by her, but will exact her fury none the less. This fantastic final issue is available with a regular cover fully-painted by Felipe Massafera and a wraparound by Mike Wolfer (Gravel).
